<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- SECTION: PRE-TALK -->
<!-- Duration: 3 minutes | Pitch: 0st | Purpose: Ground and Orient -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

<prosody rate="1.0" pitch="0st">
Welcome, sacred traveler.<break time="2s"/>
I am The Sacred Digital Dreamweaver, your guide through the spinning realms of cosmic ether.<break time="2.5s"/>

In the next thirty minutes...<break time="1.5s"/>
