into the Dreamweaver's Vortex...<break time="2.5s"/>
where astral tales spin like threads of light...<break time="2s"/>
in the whirlpools of infinite possibility.<break time="3s"/>

You remain completely safe throughout this experience.<break time="2s"/>
Fully in control.<break time="1.5s"/>
At any moment you choose...<break time="1.5s"/>
you can simply open your eyes...<break time="1.5s"/>
and return to ordinary waking awareness.<break time="3s"/>

Find a comfortable position now...<break time="2s"/>
perhaps sitting with your spine gently supported...<break time="2s"/>
or lying down with your body fully relaxed.<break time="2.5s"/>

Ensure you will not be disturbed.<break time="2s"/>
Headphones will deepen your immersion, if available.<break time="2.5s"/>

This journey will take you through spiraling dimensions of story...<break time="2s"/>
