The Inner Healer, who mends the fragments of your being...<break time="2s"/>
The Heart Flame Tender, who keeps the fire of your truth burning...<break time="2s"/>
and The Rose Mother, who births beauty from the soil of your soul.<break time="3s"/>

Allow yourself to <emphasis level="moderate">receive</emphasis>...<break time="2s"/>
whatever insights come naturally.<break time="2.5s"/>
In your own way...<break time="1.5s"/>
in your own time.<break time="3.5s"/>
</prosody>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
